    <item>
      <title>Keycloak 개요 및 기본 개념</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak01/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak01/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;Keycloak이란 무엇인가?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-keycloak이란-무엇인가&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-keycloak%ec%9d%b4%eb%9e%80-%eb%ac%b4%ec%97%87%ec%9d%b8%ea%b0%80&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. Keycloak 소개&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-keycloak-소개&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-keycloak-%ec%86%8c%ea%b0%9c&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keycloak은 &lt;strong&gt;오픈소스 Identity and Access Management (IAM)&lt;/strong&gt; 솔루션입니다. 인증(Authentication), 권한부여(Authorization), 사용자 관리(User Management)를 손쉽게 통합할 수 있도록 도와줍니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Keycloak 아키텍처 이해</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak02/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak02/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;Keycloak 전체 컴포넌트 구조&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-keycloak-전체-컴포넌트-구조&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-keycloak-%ec%a0%84%ec%b2%b4-%ec%bb%b4%ed%8f%ac%eb%84%8c%ed%8a%b8-%ea%b5%ac%ec%a1%b0&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. Keycloak 구성 요소 개요&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-keycloak-구성-요소-개요&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-keycloak-%ea%b5%ac%ec%84%b1-%ec%9a%94%ec%86%8c-%ea%b0%9c%ec%9a%94&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keycloak은 인증/인가를 처리하기 위한 &lt;strong&gt;모듈화된 구조&lt;/strong&gt;를 갖고 있으며, 다음과 같은 주요 컴포넌트들로 구성됩니다:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Keycloak 설치 및 구성</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak03/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak03/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;Standalone 모드 설치&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-standalone-모드-설치&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-standalone-%eb%aa%a8%eb%93%9c-%ec%84%a4%ec%b9%98&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. 기본 설치 환경&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-기본-설치-환경&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-%ea%b8%b0%eb%b3%b8-%ec%84%a4%ec%b9%98-%ed%99%98%ea%b2%bd&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keycloak은 Java 기반이며, 기본적으로 &lt;strong&gt;Standalone 모드&lt;/strong&gt;로 동작할 수 있습니다. 개발, 테스트, POC 환경에서는 가장 빠르고 간단한 방식입니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Realm, Client, Role, User 구조</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak04/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak04/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;Realm: 멀티 테넌시 개념&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-realm-멀티-테넌시-개념&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-realm-%eb%a9%80%ed%8b%b0-%ed%85%8c%eb%84%8c%ec%8b%9c-%ea%b0%9c%eb%85%90&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. Realm이란?&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-realm이란&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-realm%ec%9d%b4%eb%9e%80&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Realm&lt;/strong&gt;은 Keycloak에서 인증 및 권한 부여를 독립적으로 관리할 수 있는 &lt;strong&gt;보안 도메인&lt;/strong&gt;입니다. 하나의 Keycloak 서버에서 여러 개의 Realm을 만들 수 있으며, 서로 완전히 격리됩니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>인증(Authentication) 구성</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak05/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak05/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;Keycloak Login Flow 이해&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-keycloak-login-flow-이해&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-keycloak-login-flow-%ec%9d%b4%ed%95%b4&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. 기본 Login Flow란?&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-기본-login-flow란&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-%ea%b8%b0%eb%b3%b8-login-flow%eb%9e%80&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keycloak에서 인증 절차는 &lt;strong&gt;Login Flow&lt;/strong&gt;라는 이름으로 구성되며, 사용자가 로그인할 때 어떤 과정을 거칠지를 정의합니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>인가(Authorization) 구성</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak06/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak06/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;Keycloak Authorization Services 이해&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-keycloak-authorization-services-이해&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-keycloak-authorization-services-%ec%9d%b4%ed%95%b4&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. Keycloak의 인가 서비스란?&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-keycloak의-인가-서비스란&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-keycloak%ec%9d%98-%ec%9d%b8%ea%b0%80-%ec%84%9c%eb%b9%84%ec%8a%a4%eb%9e%80&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keycloak은 단순한 인증(로그인)뿐 아니라, 리소스 접근을 세밀하게 제어하는 &lt;strong&gt;Authorization Service&lt;/strong&gt;를 제공합니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Keycloak과 외부 시스템 연동</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak07/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak07/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;LDAP / Active Directory 연동&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-ldap--active-directory-연동&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-ldap--active-directory-%ec%97%b0%eb%8f%99&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. Keycloak과 LDAP 연동 개요&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-keycloak과-ldap-연동-개요&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-keycloak%ea%b3%bc-ldap-%ec%97%b0%eb%8f%99-%ea%b0%9c%ec%9a%94&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keycloak은 외부 디렉토리 서버(예: OpenLDAP, Microsoft AD)와 쉽게 연동할 수 있도록 &lt;strong&gt;User Federation&lt;/strong&gt; 기능을 제공합니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Keycloak과 OAuth2 / OIDC</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak08/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak08/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;Authorization Code Flow&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-authorization-code-flow&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-authorization-code-flow&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. OAuth2 Authorization Code Flow란?&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-oauth2-authorization-code-flow란&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-oauth2-authorization-code-flow%eb%9e%80&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;사용자가 Keycloak을 통해 로그인하면, 애플리케이션이 &lt;strong&gt;Authorization Code&lt;/strong&gt;를 받고, 이를 통해 &lt;strong&gt;Access Token&lt;/strong&gt;을 발급받는 표준적인 인증 방식입니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>테마 및 UI 커스터마이징</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak09/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/devops/keycloak/keycloak09/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2&gt;1️⃣ &lt;strong&gt;로그인/계정 화면 커스터마이징&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-로그인계정-화면-커스터마이징&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-%eb%a1%9c%ea%b7%b8%ec%9d%b8%ea%b3%84%ec%a0%95-%ed%99%94%eb%a9%b4-%ec%bb%a4%ec%8a%a4%ed%84%b0%eb%a7%88%ec%9d%b4%ec%a7%95&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1. Keycloak 기본 로그인 화면&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;1-keycloak-기본-로그인-화면&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;#1-keycloak-%ea%b8%b0%eb%b3%b8-%eb%a1%9c%ea%b7%b8%ec%9d%b8-%ed%99%94%eb%a9%b4&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Keycloak은 기본적으로 아래와 같은 로그인 화면을 제공합니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
